I think the valet parking at the hotel is around the same amount and you can take your car in and out as needed.	Also, if you are planning on parking your car there is only valet parking available which at $35 per day is quite pricey.	We enjoyed a buffet breakfast at the hotel restaurant on Sunday morning and then we called the valet parking to get our cars (two cars for the 8 of us).	Very easy to get to - but parking is an issue and the rate of $35.00 / day is very steep.